<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2016-08-11</DATELINE><TITLE>Synthesis and Antiviral Activity of Several N-Containing 5α-STEROIDS</TITLE><BODY>A study of the antiviral activity of several new hydrazones and amines and amides of 5α-steroids that were synthesized by us earlier found highly and moderately active compounds. The structures of the synthesized compounds were proven using IR, PMR, (13)C NMR, and mass spectral data.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>